  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for bind",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for bind fixes the following issues:\n\nUpgrade to release 9.20.15:\n\n- CVE-2025-8677: DNSSEC validation fails if matching but invalid DNSKEY is found (bsc#1252378).\n- CVE-2025-40778: Address various spoofing attacks (bsc#1252379).\n- CVE-2025-40780: Cache-poisoning due to weak pseudo-random number generator (bsc#1252380).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
